com.google.api.gax.protobuf

Class Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.gax.protobuf.Type

  • public abstract class Type
extends Object
    Represents the type of a protocol buffer value. Reflects the type system used by Expression, and is able to represented primitive types, repeated types, and maps.
